{% comment %}
  ============================================
  PAUZE SCIENCE — "The Science Behind"
  ============================================
  Replica el bloque "The Science Behind URO" de O Positiv:
  - H2 grande
  - Video o placeholder
  - 2 columnas: "El problema" / "Cómo te ayuda"
  
  USAR EN: PDP (después del bloque de compra)
{% endcomment %}

<section class="pauze-page pauze-section pauze-section--cacao pauze-science">
  <div class="pauze-science__glow"></div>
  <div class="pauze-container">
    <div class="pauze-section__header pauze-reveal">
      <span class="pauze-eyebrow pauze-eyebrow--gold">{{ section.settings.eyebrow | default: 'La ciencia detrás' }}</span>
      <h2 class="pauze-h2">{{ section.settings.heading | default: 'Cómo Pauze trabaja en tu cuerpo' }}</h2>
      {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
        <p class="pauze-section__sub">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    {%- if section.settings.video_url != blank -%}
      <div class="pauze-science__video pauze-reveal">
        <video controls poster="{{ section.settings.video_poster | image_url: width: 1600 }}">
          <source src="{{ section.settings.video_url }}" type="video/mp4">
        </video>
      </div>
    {%- else -%}
      <div class="pauze-science__video-placeholder pauze-reveal">
        <div class="pauze-science__play-btn">▶</div>
        <p class="pauze-science__placeholder-text">[Video explicativo · 60-90 segundos · subimos cuando esté grabado]</p>
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}

    <div class="pauze-science__cols pauze-reveal">
      <div class="pauze-science__col">
        <div class="pauze-science__col-num pauze-science__col-num--gold">01</div>
        <h3 class="pauze-h3">{{ section.settings.col1_title | default: 'El problema' }}</h3>
        <p>{{ section.settings.col1_text | default: 'Cuando tu día estuvo lleno de pantallas, decisiones y estímulos, tu sistema nervioso queda en modo alerta. El cortisol no baja, la mente no se apaga, y el cuerpo no entra en modo descanso aunque estés cansado/a.' }}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pauze-science__divider">
        <svg width="100" height="20" viewBox="0 0 100 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M 0 10 L 100 10" stroke="#C9954E" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="2,4"/>
          <circle cx="50" cy="10" r="6" fill="#C9954E"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="pauze-science__col">
        <div class="pauze-science__col-num pauze-science__col-num--green">02</div>
        <h3 class="pauze-h3">{{ section.settings.col2_title | default: 'Cómo te ayuda' }}</h3>
        <p>{{ section.settings.col2_text | default: 'Pauze combina L-teanina (que activa ondas alpha de relajación), apigenina (que se une a receptores GABA igual que la manzanilla) y magnesio glicinato (que relaja la musculatura). Tres activos clínicos, dosis honestas, sin melatonina.' }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- if section.settings.cta_text != blank -%}
      <div class="pauze-text-center pauze-mt-4">
        <a href="{{ section.settings.cta_link }}" class="pauze-btn pauze-btn--crema">{{ section.settings.cta_text }}</a>
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.pauze-science {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.pauze-science__glow {
  position: absolute;
  top: -150px;
  right: -150px;
  width: 500px;
  height: 500px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(93, 170, 63, 0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.pauze-science__video {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  border-radius: 20px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: var(--pauze-shadow-lg);
}
.pauze-science__video video { display: block; width: 100%; }
.pauze-science__video-placeholder {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  aspect-ratio: 16/9;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A3422 0%, #3D2C1F 100%);
  border-radius: 20px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
  position: relative;
}
.pauze-science__play-btn {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--pauze-verde);
  color: white;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 2rem;
  padding-left: 0.4rem;
  animation: pauze-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 20px rgba(59, 122, 44, 0.1);
}
.pauze-science__placeholder-text {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--pauze-beige);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.pauze-science__cols {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 2rem;
  max-width: 920px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  align-items: center;
}
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .pauze-science__cols {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }
}
.pauze-science__col p {
  color: var(--pauze-beige);
  line-height: 1.7;
  font-size: 0.98rem;
  margin: 0.65rem 0 0;
}
.pauze-science__col-num {
  font-family: var(--pauze-font-display);
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 3rem;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.pauze-science__col-num--gold { color: var(--pauze-dorado); }
.pauze-science__col-num--green { color: var(--pauze-verde-bright); }
.pauze-science__divider {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  opacity: 0.7;
}
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .pauze-science__divider { transform: rotate(90deg); }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Pauze: The Science Behind",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eyebrow",
      "label": "Eyebrow",
      "default": "La ciencia detrás"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Título H2",
      "default": "Cómo Pauze trabaja en tu cuerpo"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "subheading",
      "label": "Subtítulo"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "video_url",
      "label": "URL del video (mp4)"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "video_poster",
      "label": "Poster del video"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Columna 1: El problema"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "col1_title",
      "label": "Título",
      "default": "El problema"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "col1_text",
      "label": "Texto",
      "default": "Cuando tu día estuvo lleno de pantallas, decisiones y estímulos, tu sistema nervioso queda en modo alerta. El cortisol no baja, la mente no se apaga, y el cuerpo no entra en modo descanso aunque estés cansado/a."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Columna 2: Cómo te ayuda"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "col2_title",
      "label": "Título",
      "default": "Cómo te ayuda"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "col2_text",
      "label": "Texto",
      "default": "Pauze combina L-teanina (que activa ondas alpha de relajación), apigenina (que se une a receptores GABA igual que la manzanilla) y magnesio glicinato (que relaja la musculatura). Tres activos clínicos, dosis honestas, sin melatonina."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "CTA opcional"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cta_text",
      "label": "CTA"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "cta_link",
      "label": "Link CTA"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Pauze: Science Behind"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
